into left 5 and back, up and 80.

01:14.376 --> 01:15.626
Watch out, left 5 and back.

01:15.917 --> 01:19.709
Right 6 and left 2 full gear,
release for 50 then right 6.

01:20.084 --> 01:22.458
Invisible, cut to
left 2 and cut to right 3

01:22.459 --> 01:24.792
into U-turn 200 left 7.

01:25.042 --> 01:27.458
