01:27.459 --> 01:30.542
left 4 and right 4, straight 100 meter

01:30.626 --> 01:31.875
This is the dangerous post-slope

01:31.876 --> 01:34.584
left 4 then right 4,
straight 100 meter.

01:36.167 --> 01:36.751
ladies and gentlemen

01:36.752 --> 01:39.208
This is the final stage of the

01:39.209 --> 01:40.792
2022 China Rally Championship.

01:40.959 --> 01:43.125
Xu Tailang has taken

01:43.126 --> 01:45.251
a commanding lead!

01:45.501 --> 01:47.833
Last year, Lang won the first stage

01:47.834 --> 01:49.751
as a low-ranked driver.

01:50.001 --> 01:51.541
Who could have predicted
this eye-popping performance

01:51.542 --> 01:53.209
after he transferred teams?

01:53.501 --> 01:54.084
Lang!

01:54.334 --> 01:57.126
He has taken the rally world by storm!

02:11.001 --> 02:12.209
Oil temperature?

02:12.292 --> 02:13.959
Oil, 100 normal.

02:15.417 --> 02:16.542
3.5 bar turbo boost,

02:16.667 --> 02:18.542
push the Anti-Lag to the max.

04:03.417 --> 04:05.876
I'd first like to thank
my crew and sponsors.

04:07.542 --> 04:09.209
I'd also like to thank my co-driver,

04:09.501 --> 04:11.001
who's always got my back!

04:11.084 --> 04:11.459
C'mon,

04:11.501 --> 04:13.001
let's get a shot of him!

04:16.875 --> 04:18.791
Finally, I want to thank

04:18.959 --> 04:21.416
the most important person in my life.

04:21.666 --> 04:23.209
I know he's here, somewhere.

04:23.251 --> 04:24.667
I want to tell him...

04:27.084 --> 04:28.001
Dad...

04:28.834 --> 04:29.917
Thank you.

04:31.751 --> 04:33.209
Thank you...

04:34.042 --> 04:36.042
For being ever so supportive.

04:36.626 --> 04:37.876
Thank you...

04:38.626 --> 04:40.626
For discouraging my dreams.

04:41.167 --> 04:44.417
And thank you for disrespecting my career.

04:45.834 --> 04:48.001
I invited you here today

04:48.334 --> 04:50.251
to prove you were wrong.

04:50.917 --> 04:53.417
I'm the champion.

04:53.751 --> 04:55.126
I've made it.

04:57.251 --> 04:59.001
Interesting words for your father.

04:59.042 --> 05:00.001
What about your mother?

05:00.042 --> 05:01.667
I never met her.

05:03.209 --> 05:04.709
She died after my birth.

05:05.251 --> 05:06.584
I'm sorry.

05:07.917 --> 05:08.709
Alright.

05:08.751 --> 05:10.376
Thank you, that's all.

05:12.876 --> 05:20.542
Lang!

05:30.959 --> 05:32.209
Congratulations.

05:33.209 --> 05:36.001
You didn't have to dress up.

05:41.792 --> 05:43.459
When you first learned to drive,

05:43.584 --> 05:45.959
I never thought you'd turn out this good.

05:48.251 --> 05:50.876
You always forced me to do stuff I hated.

05:51.709 --> 05:53.084
First, math.

05:53.209 --> 05:54.959
Then medicine.

05:55.876 --> 05:57.876
And when I told you I loved driving,

05:58.001 --> 06:00.251
You made me an ambulance driver.

06:01.126 --> 06:02.542
Before she died, your mother said

06:02.959 --> 06:05.834
It'd be great if you could become a doctor.

06:05.876 --> 06:07.542
Did she also say it'd be great

06:07.626 --> 06:09.626
if her husband got into some fucked up shit

06:09.709 --> 06:11.292
and got locked up for six years

06:11.417 --> 06:14.209
right before she gave birth?

06:17.709 --> 06:18.417
Follow me.

06:47.209 --> 06:48.417
Slow down, Lang...

06:48.459 --> 06:49.126
Not too fast...

06:49.167 --> 06:50.001
Careful...

07:04.292 --> 07:05.667
I'm gonna be sick.

07:05.834 --> 07:06.917
Go ahead.

07:07.084 --> 07:08.626
That's my co-driver's anyways.

07:36.084 --> 07:37.001
There was someone else in the car!

07:37.002 --> 07:39.334
They say right before you die...

07:41.667 --> 07:44.917
your whole life flashes in front of you.

07:46.459 --> 07:48.292
Let's see.

07:59.334 --> 08:01.251
"Have a sip, son."

08:07.417 --> 08:10.876
"What are these good for?"

08:19.292 --> 08:21.584
"Is this your signature?"

08:27.542 --> 08:28.834
"Boy, what you looking at?"

08:32.833 --> 08:35.251
"Mom..."

08:39.501 --> 08:41.126
"Lang, I love you."

08:43.501 --> 08:45.334
"Sorry..."

08:47.834 --> 08:50.292
"I found someone else."

09:00.542 --> 09:03.251
"How do you feel?"

09:07.584 --> 09:09.667
"It's my first time. Pretty nervous."

09:15.792 --> 09:17.292
"Fucking idiot! You crashed
on a straightaway!"

09:17.876 --> 09:20.084
"I quit!"

09:22.751 --> 09:24.167
"That was your last chance!"

09:27.334 --> 09:29.292
"Get out!"

09:31.334 --> 09:34.126
"I got you a job driving an ambulance."

09:40.959 --> 09:42.376
"Emergency Medical Dispatch speaking."

09:42.417 --> 09:43.667
"We need an ambulance."

09:48.376 --> 09:50.126
"Didn't take you long to fuck that up!"

09:52.459 --> 09:54.417
"Cheer up..."

09:59.501 --> 10:00.959
"Oops..."

10:06.584 --> 10:08.542
"Stop drinking,
and you can drive for my boss."

10:14.584 --> 10:15.751
"Drive!"

10:24.334 --> 10:26.501
"You drive well!"

10:28.209 --> 10:31.709
"This rally car's yours."

10:46.292 --> 10:48.501
"Steady, almost there!"

11:00.626 --> 11:02.834
"Mom, this is for you."

13:29.542 --> 13:30.834
Mrs. Chen?

13:34.917 --> 13:37.001
I'm sorry, do I know you?

13:37.167 --> 13:38.542
I was Class of 2004.

13:38.584 --> 13:39.459
Xu Tailang.

13:39.542 --> 13:40.959
You were my teacher.

13:41.084 --> 13:42.626
You used to tell me.

13:42.751 --> 13:43.792
Tailang, oh Tailang...

13:43.834 --> 13:45.542
Don't be so headstrong...

13:45.709 --> 13:47.126
Class of 2004?

13:47.209 --> 13:48.709
It's 1998.

13:48.959 --> 13:50.042
Weirdo...

13:53.542 --> 13:54.667
1998?

13:55.209 --> 13:56.501
1998...

13:56.626 --> 13:57.626
Really?

13:58.001 --> 13:59.959
Thief!

14:23.334 --> 14:24.126
I'm already dead.

14:24.167 --> 14:25.584
Why should I be afraid?

14:42.376 --> 14:43.751
Fucking Batman?

15:05.876 --> 15:07.126
Isn't that a little unfair?

15:17.001 --> 15:17.584
Don't get excited.

15:30.792 --> 15:31.501
Take off my belt!

15:31.876 --> 15:32.959
My belt!

15:33.459 --> 15:34.376
Quickly!

15:37.501 --> 15:38.501
Tie him up!

15:50.584 --> 15:51.417
Dad?

15:52.667 --> 15:53.376
Dad?

15:55.084 --> 15:55.959
Police!

15:57.751 --> 15:58.709
What are you doing?

15:59.167 --> 15:59.917
Brother

16:00.501 --> 16:01.417
We'll meet again.

16:04.751 --> 16:05.834
Stop!

16:15.334 --> 16:17.376
It's been hours,

16:17.959 --> 16:20.626
and you still haven't told
me where you're from.

16:22.792 --> 16:24.751
I already did!

16:24.876 --> 16:26.167
You just don't get it.

16:26.209 --> 16:27.376
This is your ID?

16:27.417 --> 16:28.959
Yea, obviously.

16:31.959 --> 16:33.376
This is a fucking ID.

16:33.501 --> 16:35.001
See?

16:38.126 --> 16:39.792
What year were you born?

16:40.084 --> 16:41.251
I...

16:44.042 --> 16:44.792
Next year.

16:47.709 --> 16:49.459
You think because you
helped us catch a bad guy

16:49.501 --> 16:51.834
We're all close and shit now.

16:53.042 --> 16:54.876
You may have the right to remain silent,

16:54.959 --> 16:57.459
but you don't have the right
to bullshit me, got it?

16:58.417 --> 16:59.292
Where the hell are you from?

16:59.376 --> 17:01.251
I told you, from here!

17:01.626 --> 17:02.917
Take me to where you live.

17:03.667 --> 17:05.376
If no one can vouch for you,

17:05.584 --> 17:07.251
I'll send you straight to the nut house.

17:09.834 --> 17:13.251
I can't make 24 with these cards...

17:16.666 --> 17:18.001
I can't do it.

17:22.376 --> 17:23.791
Boss, you keep losing.

17:40.292 --> 17:42.626
You don't have to kill yourself
just because you can't do the math!

17:45.667 --> 17:46.376
Sir...

17:46.834 --> 17:48.084
What's up with the diver?

17:48.792 --> 17:49.792
You know him.

17:49.834 --> 17:50.792
That's Liu Yi.

17:50.834 --> 17:52.292
He and his pops are street vendors.

17:52.792 --> 17:55.001
They're terrified of the cops.

17:55.126 --> 17:56.084
Wu Yi's son?

17:56.167 --> 17:57.001
Yeah.

17:57.334 --> 17:58.126
He shot up quickly.

17:58.251 --> 17:59.251
Yeah.

18:00.376 --> 18:01.209
And who are you?

18:02.376 --> 18:03.501
Officer, my name is Ma.

18:03.584 --> 18:05.959
Zheng's been looking after me.

18:06.667 --> 18:07.667
What do you do?

18:07.834 --> 18:09.626
Programming and software development.

18:10.417 --> 18:11.917
So, unemployed.

18:12.459 --> 18:13.251
Get out of here.

18:18.751 --> 18:19.709
Do you know this man?

18:20.251 --> 18:21.334
How are you two related?

18:26.001 --> 18:27.042
Big brother!

18:29.584 --> 18:30.792
Sir...

18:31.001 --> 18:32.126
Don't "Sir" me.

18:32.292 --> 18:33.708
Just 'cause you've got a video hall

18:33.709 --> 18:34.584
with some Hong Kong movies...

18:34.959 --> 18:36.459
This is our Chief...

18:36.542 --> 18:37.167
Call him Chief.

18:37.376 --> 18:38.042
Chief...

18:38.167 --> 18:38.917
Show some respect.

18:38.959 --> 18:39.709
Save it.

18:39.876 --> 18:41.376
Who is he?

18:43.542 --> 18:44.084
Brother...

18:44.584 --> 18:45.251
Yeah?

18:45.626 --> 18:47.792
It's the anniversary of dad's death.
Where've you been?

18:48.459 --> 18:50.626
Get in there and pay your respects to him!

18:51.459 --> 18:52.084
Yes, yes.

18:52.209 --> 18:53.709
Hold on, hold on!

18:53.792 --> 18:55.167
Keep your mouth shut.

18:56.917 --> 18:58.959
What's your father's name?

19:01.001 --> 19:03.042
Shit, Gramps died when I was little.
I don't remember his name.

19:04.167 --> 19:05.709
What are you mumbling about?

19:07.167 --> 19:07.792
Sir...

19:08.292 --> 19:09.834
My brother Zheng...

19:10.792 --> 19:12.417
He was always my dad's favorite.

19:12.709 --> 19:13.792
He never really liked me,

19:14.126 --> 19:16.209
so I left home early to make it on my own.

19:16.542 --> 19:18.084
To be honest,

19:19.376 --> 19:21.292
his death never really felt like a loss,

19:21.501 --> 19:24.084
because he never loved me.

19:24.376 --> 19:25.417
It's true.

19:25.709 --> 19:28.376
Go inside and check if
you don't believe me.

19:29.126 --> 19:30.709
He's wearing a checkered
shirt in his portrait.

19:31.542 --> 19:33.542
His ashes are next to the TV in a red urn.

19:33.584 --> 19:35.209
The TV is covered by a white cloth.

19:35.251 --> 19:36.542
Go and see for yourself.

19:37.834 --> 19:40.709
Fine, wait here.

19:45.584 --> 19:47.251
How do you know my name?

19:47.417 --> 19:48.584
It's written on your forehead.

19:51.459 --> 19:53.209
What are you scheming about?

19:53.334 --> 19:54.542
Come here.

19:55.126 --> 19:56.417
Tell me,

19:56.751 --> 19:59.334
what brand is your TV?

20:03.959 --> 20:05.042
Hitachi...

20:05.501 --> 20:09.084
Or is it Toshiba?

20:11.584 --> 20:13.251
What's the brand?

20:13.667 --> 20:14.292
Hitachi!

20:14.376 --> 20:16.292
Everything else checks out.

20:18.501 --> 20:19.376
You're a lousy son.

20:22.042 --> 20:23.167
Take care, Chief Jin!

20:23.251 --> 20:24.251
Take care, Chief Jin!

20:29.126 --> 20:30.292
Come with me.

20:45.667 --> 20:47.292
When did you sneak into my house?

20:48.167 --> 20:49.334
You know it so well.

20:49.959 --> 20:50.792
I...

20:52.001 --> 20:53.167
Buddy,

20:54.042 --> 20:55.626
Quit stealing.

21:00.709 --> 21:01.334
Okay.

21:01.917 --> 21:02.792
What's your name?

21:03.167 --> 21:04.251
Xu Tailang.

21:04.334 --> 21:05.417
But you can just call me Lang.

21:06.001 --> 21:07.167
What was your dad thinking,

21:07.584 --> 21:09.084
giving you such a stupid name?

21:09.334 --> 21:10.292
Tailang?

21:10.501 --> 21:11.334
Tailang...

21:12.542 --> 21:14.084
Your dad's an idiot.

21:19.959 --> 21:20.959
You know, given his IQ,

21:20.960 --> 21:22.876
to produce a son this awesome...

21:24.042 --> 21:26.001
My mother must've been pretty smart.

21:28.667 --> 21:30.251
I can meet my mom...

21:31.667 --> 21:33.334
I can meet my mom!

21:34.584 --> 21:35.709
Hey, are you married?

21:36.001 --> 21:36.959
What's her name?

21:38.376 --> 21:40.792
You haven't even asked my name
and you want hers...

21:41.042 --> 21:42.501
What are you after?

21:42.626 --> 21:44.001
So used to stealing,

21:44.126 --> 21:45.626
you wanna steal her too?

21:45.650 --> 21:46.875
Aah..yah...

21:46.876 --> 21:47.251
My bad...

21:47.334 --> 21:48.334
Okay Zheng,

21:48.501 --> 21:49.792
What's your full name?

21:51.251 --> 21:51.751
It's funny.

21:52.376 --> 21:53.084
We have the same surname.

21:54.417 --> 21:55.084
Xu Zhengtai.

21:56.542 --> 21:57.709
Not bad, huh?

21:57.917 --> 21:58.959
My dad was smart, right?

21:59.001 --> 22:00.876
Gave me a great name.

22:01.584 --> 22:04.584
That's why I call my
gang the Zhengtai Gang.

22:04.626 --> 22:05.626
Awesome, right?

22:05.792 --> 22:06.459
Join us.

22:07.459 --> 22:09.542
I'll introduce you to my girl.

22:10.001 --> 22:11.292
I'm in!

22:12.251 --> 22:14.709
Hey, didn't one of your guys
just jump into the river?

22:15.167 --> 22:16.001
Oh, it's fine.

22:18.001 --> 22:18.667
Mumu!

22:18.959 --> 22:19.584
Mumu!

22:20.084 --> 22:21.209
Mumu!

22:22.542 --> 22:23.792
Mumu, come here!

22:24.209 --> 22:25.584
Mumu, come here!

22:26.376 --> 22:27.459
Oh, there you are!

22:28.834 --> 22:30.167
Easy, Mumu. Good boy.

22:30.376 --> 22:31.876
Go find Liu Yi.

22:32.584 --> 22:33.334
Go!

22:35.167 --> 22:36.709
He's a Golden Retriever.

22:37.334 --> 22:38.584
The first in town.

22:38.709 --> 22:39.959
And the only in town.

22:40.376 --> 22:42.084
They're used as search dogs abroad.

22:42.751 --> 22:43.501
You'll see.

22:44.542 --> 22:45.751
Mumu!

22:46.001 --> 22:47.000
Mumu...

22:47.084 --> 22:47.667
Mumu...

22:47.917 --> 22:48.792
Mumu!

22:50.459 --> 22:51.167
Mumu...

22:53.334 --> 22:54.459
Mumu...

22:54.584 --> 22:55.251
Mumu!

22:55.792 --> 22:56.459
Mumu...

22:58.042 --> 22:58.709
Mumu...

23:00.542 --> 23:01.876
Louder!

23:01.959 --> 23:03.417
It's because of you Mumu got lost!

23:04.167 --> 23:04.917
Mumu!

23:05.417 --> 23:06.334
Louder!

23:06.376 --> 23:07.126
Mumu!

23:09.626 --> 23:10.667
Mumu!

23:27.376 --> 23:29.542
Mumu, how'd you get so skinny?

23:30.042 --> 23:32.001
That's clearly not Mumu.

23:32.167 --> 23:33.126
Wait, Lang.

23:33.667 --> 23:34.292
Look.

23:34.626 --> 23:35.542
That guy...

23:35.876 --> 23:38.542
The one in the middle is Luo Li.

23:38.792 --> 23:40.417
Our sworn enemy.

23:40.501 --> 23:43.001
Didn't realize he'd gotten into
the car smuggling business.

23:44.917 --> 23:46.917
These rats are armed with guns, boss.

23:47.001 --> 23:48.584
Should we load some cannons?

23:49.751 --> 23:51.751
That can't be a real gun.

23:52.126 --> 23:53.501
Real or fake, we ain't afraid.

24:00.501 --> 24:02.459
Well, if it's okay,
can I get going?

24:02.584 --> 24:04.667
I'm halfway through coding a program.

24:05.209 --> 24:06.876
Coding a program?

24:10.834 --> 24:12.459
Hey, let's go eat at my girl's place!

24:12.501 --> 24:12.751
Okay.

24:17.584 --> 24:18.251
Lang,

24:18.292 --> 24:19.834
My girl makes quite the fish

24:21.959 --> 24:23.042
Here comes the fish!

24:26.042 --> 24:26.751
Oops

24:26.792 --> 24:28.376
Oh, I forgot vinegar.

24:28.959 --> 24:29.626
C'mon,

24:30.209 --> 24:31.584
it's just a fish.

24:32.251 --> 24:33.292
Lang...

24:34.501 --> 24:35.542
She is coming...

24:35.751 --> 24:36.917
Hurry!

24:42.501 --> 24:43.084
Hot, too hot!

24:45.834 --> 24:46.626
Ma'am...

24:47.001 --> 24:48.251
Just call me Hua.

24:48.501 --> 24:49.376
What's your full name?

24:49.501 --> 24:50.751
Leave it! Hua is good.

24:50.834 --> 24:51.959
I don't like my real name.

24:52.501 --> 24:53.584
Just call me Hua.

24:53.626 --> 24:54.667
Names come from our parents.

24:54.751 --> 24:56.584
It's not your fault.

24:56.709 --> 24:57.584
What's your name?

24:59.417 --> 25:00.292
Niu Aihua.

25:00.376 --> 25:01.917
You're better off with just Hua.

25:04.626 --> 25:06.792
I have no recollections of my mother,

25:07.126 --> 25:09.876
except for some blurry
black and white photos.

25:10.459 --> 25:11.917
When I was born,

25:12.001 --> 25:13.792
my dad was already locked up.

25:14.501 --> 25:16.626
My mom's name was Zhang Suzhen,

25:17.126 --> 25:18.376
not Niu Aihua.

25:19.501 --> 25:21.584
But their faces are kinda similar.

25:22.334 --> 25:25.584
Seems like my dad has a type.

25:27.126 --> 25:27.751
No!

25:28.584 --> 25:30.959
I can't let this go on.

25:31.417 --> 25:33.001
I've got to find my mom, Zhang Suzhen,

25:33.084 --> 25:34.501
and introduce her to my dad.

25:34.792 --> 25:36.626
Otherwise,

25:37.542 --> 25:39.376
I won't exist anymore!

25:41.542 --> 25:43.751
How serious are you two?

25:44.292 --> 25:45.209
We're getting married next month.

25:46.959 --> 25:47.584
Have a drink.

25:47.626 --> 25:48.417
C'mon.

25:51.459 --> 25:52.792
Marriage is a big step.

25:53.209 --> 25:54.417
You should really take it seriously.

25:54.709 --> 25:57.376
It takes at least a year
or two to truly know someone...

25:57.709 --> 25:59.209
To know what you're getting into...

25:59.709 --> 26:01.126
How long have you known each other?

26:01.209 --> 26:02.042
Over twenty years.

26:05.042 --> 26:07.417
I wasn't even four years old
when I met Hua for the first time.

26:07.501 --> 26:08.751
I was living next door.

26:08.792 --> 26:10.167
Her mom had just given birth

26:10.501 --> 26:11.501
and was breastfeeding her.

26:11.709 --> 26:12.459
It was love at first sight.

26:12.542 --> 26:13.667
What do you know at four?

26:13.834 --> 26:15.542
A lot. I knew I wasn't three.

26:15.792 --> 26:16.542
Right.

26:20.084 --> 26:21.209
I'll get it!

26:23.001 --> 26:24.084
You got it?

26:24.334 --> 26:24.917
Found it!

26:25.042 --> 26:25.917
Muah...

26:28.626 --> 26:30.751
They really are in love.

26:31.251 --> 26:33.542
Seems like I have no choice
but to step in myself.

26:34.001 --> 26:36.667
Dad, forgive me.

